If you have any type of food allergies BEWARE.  I used to frequent this place but after my experience today I won’t ever go back. I always stay away from egg for a reason, yes shocker it’s a breakfast place but they’ve always been very accommodating to me in the past. Today, the server (forgot her name) not only did it seem like she was rushing me to put my order in was also not helpful. I asked about two different dishes, both sandwiches if they could not put egg on it or even leave it on the side. The server told me she needed to ask her manager if they could modify any dishes and when she came back she said no. How am I changing a dish when I just asked to keep one ingredient out? I  tried to order different items literally to have no egg or just leave it on the side and she wasn’t helpful nor was the so called manager. (She was tall, thin, and blonde) This place really needs to re-evaluate how to handle customers who have food allergies. Manager ended up ringing us up and was not even friendly nor did she bother to apologize. She knew what table i was sitting at the entire time. A restaurant truly reflects its management and let me tell you, I will never go back.
